==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inflexed
<hw>In*flexed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Turned;
bent.</def> <rj><au>Feltham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Bent or turned abruptly inwards,
or toward the axis, as the petals of a flower.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inflexibility</ent>⟦br⟧
